yna]], 0.17% \u2013 [[Ewa Kopacz]]}}\n| -\n| 7.36%\n| 7.89%\n| -\n| -\n| 2.62%\n| 0.44%\n| 3.93%\n| 1.27%\n| -\n|-\n| style=\"background:lightsteelblue;\" | [https://oko.press/andrzej-duda-mu-sie-uda-wygrywa-tuskiem-turze-ii-pewnie-tez/ IPSOS]\n| 19\u201321 December 2016\n| 16%\n| 1%\n| style=\"background:lightsteelblue;\" | '''36%'''\n| 1%\n| style=\"background:#FDDCB8;\" | 18%\n| 1%{{efn|Includes: 1% \u2013 [[Grzegorz Schetyna]]}}\n| 5%\n| 8%\n| -\n| -\n| 8%\n| 1%\n| -\n| -\n| -\n|-\n| style=\"background:lightsteelblue;\" | [http://www.se.pl/wiadomosci/polityka/sondaz-prezydencki-dla-sepl-kto-w-drugiej-turze-z-duda-petru-czy-tusk_777170.html Pollster]\n| 5\u20138 February 2016\n| -\n| 9%\n| style=\"background:lightsteelblue;\" | '''38%'''\n| -\n| 16%{{efn|Includes: 3% \u2013 [[Grzegorz Schetyna]]}}\n| \n| -\n| 14%\n| style=\"background:#BFE2FF;\" | 17%\n| -\n| 3%\n| -\n| -\n| -\n| -\n| -\n|- style=\"background:#EFEFEF;\"\n| style=\"background:lightsteelblue;\" | [[2015 Polish presidential election|Presidential election]]\n| 10 May 2015\n| -\n| 7.3%\n| style=\"background:lightsteelblue;\"| '''34.8%'''\n| -\n| -\n| style=\"background:#FDDCB8;\" | 33.8%{{efn|[[Bronis\u0142aw Komorowski]]}}\n| -\n| 20.8%\n| -\n| -\n| -\n| -\n| -\n| 3.3%\n| -\n| -\n|}\n\n===Second round===\n====Duda v. Kidawa-B\u0142o\u0144ska====\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:85%;line-height:14px;\"\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" |Poll source\n! rowspan=\"2\" |Date(s)<br />administered\n| bgcolor=\"{{Law and Justice/meta/color}}\" |\n| bgcolor=\"{{Civic Platform/meta/color}}\" |\n! rowspan=\"2\" |Undecided/would not vote\n|-\n! [[Andrzej Duda|Duda]]<br/><small>[[Independent (politician)|IN]]</small>\n! [[Ma\u0142gorzata Kidawa-B\u0142o\u0144ska|Kidawa-B\u0142o\u0144ska]]<br/><small>[[Civic Platform|PO]]</small>\n|-\n| style=\"background:lightsteelblue;\" | [https://wiadomosci.onet.pl/kraj/wybory-prezydenckie-2020-sondaz-potrzebna-druga-tura-holownia-drugi/hz69r0v Maison & Partners]