wuPDoAhXyQ98KHZFBBoYQ6AEwAXoECAgQAQ#v=onepage&q=%22hal+clements%22+obituary+film&f=false|title=The Moving Picture World|date=April 17, 1916|publisher=World Photographic Publishing Company|via=Google Books}}</ref>''\n\n==Filmography==\n* ''[[Uncle Tom's Cabin (1913 film)]]''\n* ''[[The Grim Toll of War]]'' (1913)<ref name=wire>{{Cite web|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=um5ZAAAAMAAJ&q=%22hal+clements%22&dq=%22hal+clements%22&hl=en&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwidpbTftvDoAhWsiOAKHTuBArE4FBDoATACegQIARAO|title=Those fabulous serial heroines: their lives and films|first=Buck|last=Rainey|date=April 17, 1990|publisher=Scarecrow Press|via=pages.101, 271, 294}}</ref>\n* ''[[O'Brien Finds a Way]]'' (1914)\n* ''[[Armstrong's Wife]]'' (1915)\n* ''[[Out of the Darkness (1915 film)]]''\n* ''[[The Unknown (1915 drama film)]]''\n* ''[[The Secret Sin]]'' (1915)\n* ''[[The Immigrant (1915 film)]]''\n* ''[[The Girl Telegrapher's Nerve]]'' (1916)\n* ''[[Miss Jackie of the Army]]'' (1917)<ref>{{Cite book | url=https://books.google.com/?id=3Se6CwAAQBAJ&pg=PA150&lpg=PA150&dq=%22hal+clements%22#v=onepage |title = World War I on Film: English Language Releases through 2014|isbn = 9781476620633|last1 = Edwards|first1 = Paul M.|date = 11 March 2016}}</ref>\n* ''[[An American Live Wire]]'' (1918)<ref name=wire/>\n* ''[[Other Men's Wives]]'' (1919)\n* ''[[An Innocent Adventuress]]'' (1919)\n* ''[[The Siege of Petersburg]]''\n* ''[[The Sacrifice at the Spillway]]''<ref>{{Cite web | url=https://books.google.com/?id=5jAXAQAAMAAJ&pg=RA5-PA144&lpg=RA5-PA144&dq=%22hal+clements%22#v=onepage |title = Motion Picture|year = 1913}}</ref>\n* ''The Man Who Could Not Lose'', a Biograph film, as Jack Carter<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=JBIXAQAAMAAJ&pg=PA146&dq=%22hal+clements%22&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwj4qPC4s_DoAhVRiOAKHcsgBN4Q6AEITDAF#v=onepage&q=%22hal+clements%22&f=false|title=Motion Picture|date=April 17, 1915|publisher=Macfadden-Bartell.|via=Google Books}}</ref>\n* ''[[Seventeen (1940 film